OL,5, A Church of England priest who shared  
OL,6, "virulently antisemitic" material has  
OL,7, been barred from ministry for 12 years.
OL,9,FThe Reverend Dr Stephen Sizer, 69, was 
OL,10,Ffound by a church tribunal to have     
OL,11,Fengaged in conduct "unbecoming to the  
OL,12,Foffice and work of a clerk in Holy     
OL,13,FOrders".                               
OL,15,FThe Archbishop of Canterbury said Dr   
OL,16,FSizer's behaviour had given            
OL,17,F"encouragement to conspiracy theories  
OL,18,Fand tropes".                           
OL,20,FDr Sizer declined to comment.          
